Title: FremyCompany Math Equation Editor
Description:
A WPF Component that can import MathML and LaTeX to be edited in a WYSIWYG word processor. It is intended to allow both visual and computer-comprehensive (formula in programming language) exportation.

Scope and functionnalites are intended to be expanded over time.
